OL,6,FCardiff Rugby has served formal
OL,7,Fnotification that it intends to enter
OL,8,Fadministration.
OL,10,FA training session on Tuesday was
OL,11,Fcancelled and players and staff were
OL,12,Ftold the news at a meeting in the
OL,13,Fafternoon.
OL,15,FIt's understood players received
OL,16,Fassurances over their futures for the
OL,17,Ftime being, but the long term future
OL,18,Fremains unclear.
