OL,6,FA Notice of Intention (NOI) was filed
OL,7,Fin court on Tuesday, effectively
OL,8,Fgiving the club two weeks to explore
OL,9,Foptions.
OL,11,FIt comes just 16 months after Cardiff
OL,12,Flooked to have secured their long-term
OL,13,Ffuture, when Helford Capital Limited's
OL,14,Facquisition of a majority shareholding
OL,15,Fwas approved at a general meeting of
OL,16,Fclub members.
OL,18,FAt the time, Chair Alun Jones said the
OL,19,Fdeal gave Cardiff a "bright, exciting
OL,20,Fand secure future".
