OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union is poised to
OL,7,Fstep-in and take over the club,
OL,8,Fhowever Cardiff Rugby must enter
OL,9,Fadministration before that can happen.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the WRU said: 'We are
OL,12,Faware Cardiff Rugby have confirmed
OL,13,Fnotice of intention to appoint
OL,14,Fadministrators, and we are working
OL,15,Fclosely with the Cardiff Board and the
OL,16,Fadministrators to safeguard the future
OL,17,Fof professional rugby in Cardiff.'
