OL,6,FThe latest development, though, will
OL,7,Fsend shockwaves through the sport and
OL,8,Ffollows former English Premiership
OL,9,Fclubs Worcester, Wasps and London
OL,10,FIrish entering administration during
OL,11,Fthe 2022-23 season.
OL,13,FCardiff play in the United Rugby
OL,14,FChampionship and are next due to be in
OL,15,Faction on April 19 as part of Welsh
OL,16,Frugby's Judgement Day at the
OL,17,FPrincipality Stadium, when Cardiff
OL,18,Fface the Ospreys and Dragons tackle
OL,19,Fthe Scarlets.
